Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.37,0:22:32.93,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}就像是那地球仪上各种谜团　都一一解说开来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.07,0:22:36.64,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}大家就能随心所欲地到处旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.76,0:22:39.12,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}想一直到时间尽头Boooon!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.19,0:22:43.44,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}那想法像变成圆圈一样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.47,0:22:49.21,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}不管什么都要把这一切卷进幻想里面去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.44,0:22:51.92,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}在那晴空之下的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.17,0:22:54.57,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}是比魔法还更加愉快的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.61,0:22:59.88,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}永无尽头地倾注到世界　一切皆有可能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.56,0:23:05.73,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}明天再与你见面之时　带着灿烂笑容轻松哼唱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.87,0:23:08.85,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}把那些喜悦收集起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.97,0:23:11.38,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}这些其实都非常　简·单·容·易
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.46,0:23:15.98,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}赶快追上去吧　试着抓住它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.14,0:23:19.92,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}那雄伟的梦想＆梦想　你喜欢吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.23,0:01:30.27,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答えはいつも私の胸に...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.99,0:01:46.14,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,なんでだろ　あなたを選んだ私です
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.45,0:01:52.47,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もうとまらない　運命様から決められたけど
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.52,0:01:58.71,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I believe　真似だけじゃつまらないの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.81,0:02:01.04,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be right！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.39,0:02:07.49,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感じるまま感じることだけをするよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.62,0:02:14.34,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冒険でしょでしょ！ホントが嘘に変わる世界で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.37,0:02:21.19,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢があるから強くなるのよ　誰の為じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.55,0:02:24.56,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一緒に来てくださいっ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.82,0:02:30.27,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,どこまでも自由な私を見てよね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.28,0:02:35.66,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日過去になった今日のいまが奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.06,0:02:42.13,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,つかもう未来を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.37,0:02:47.76,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I believe you...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.23,0:01:30.27,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这份答案一直存在于我的内心里...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.99,0:01:46.14,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟为什么　选择你的居然会是区区的我呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.45,0:01:52.47,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已不能停步　虽然能让高贵的命运来决定一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.52,0:01:58.71,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I believe　单纯的模仿一定十分无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.81,0:02:01.04,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be right！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.39,0:02:07.49,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照着感觉走　只去做那感觉到的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.62,0:02:14.34,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冒险对吧对吧！在真实变成了谎言的世界之中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.37,0:02:21.19,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若能够拥有梦想　就可以收获坚强　并不是为了谁而去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.55,0:02:24.56,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就请你与我一起来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.82,0:02:30.27,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而看着这个无论何处都会是自由的我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.28,0:02:35.66,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在明天变成过去之前将此日此时的那奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.06,0:02:42.13,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牢牢抓住面向未来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.37,0:02:47.76,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I believe you...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.66,0:00:19.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我泡了茶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.01,0:00:20.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请用
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.97,0:00:22.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.93,0:00:31.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好喝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.66,0:00:35.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请用
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.77,0:00:37.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  朝比奈同学
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.49,0:00:42.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五月份春日建立SOS团之后光阴飞逝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.28,0:00:43.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在已经是六月了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.79,0:00:46.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实在这段时间里面
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.70,0:00:50.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经被卷入了很多将我的世界观完全推翻的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.50,0:00:51.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过那些先放在一边
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.19,0:00:53.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次是这样一个故事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.27,0:00:57.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位！我们要参加棒球大赛！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.53,0:00:59.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那天起直到今天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.30,0:01:02.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都没有发生什么值得一提的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.64,0:01:05.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都在享受着悠闲的平静与无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.30,0:01:08.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是看来那段日子也只是转瞬即逝而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.01,0:01:09.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至于为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.94,0:01:13.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要这家伙一旦这样一脸高兴地笑着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.48,0:01:16.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道为什么我就会变成疲劳的线操人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.45,0:02:55.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说要参加什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.40,0:02:56.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.05,0:03:02.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第九届室内业余棒球大赛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.93,0:03:06.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  是谁要去参加这个草地棒球赛？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.93,0:03:06.58,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（草地棒球：外行人参加的以尽兴为目的的棒球比赛）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.74,0:03:08.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是我们了！这还用问？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.94,0:03:12.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所谓的「我们」是不是把我们几个也算进去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.05,0:03:13.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还需要再找4个人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.74,0:03:18.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平时一样  是个不把对自己的想法有异议的话听进耳朵的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.79,0:03:20.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你懂棒球的规则吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.90,0:03:22.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这我当然知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.94,0:03:25.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好歹我也是尝试参加过棒球社的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.16,0:03:26.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多少懂一点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.89,0:03:29.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然因为一点意思都没有所以很快就回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.68,0:03:33.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我们为什么还非要参加\N这种「一点意思都没有」的棒球大赛？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.93,0:03:37.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是让全天下知道我们存在的大好机会啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.49,0:03:39.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能在比赛中获胜的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.21,0:03:43.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许SOS团的名号能够一举独步天下呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.36,0:03:44.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机会难得啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.19,0:03:46.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个好主意吧  实玖{\fe128\fnDFMaruMoji-W7\b0\fs24}瑠{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.22,0:03:48.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？可  可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.77,0:03:50.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？棒球很不错吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.94,0:03:53.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先说清楚  我们的目标是最终胜利！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.43,0:03:57.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一场比赛都不许输！因为我最讨厌失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.19,0:04:00.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.51,0:04:02.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有何不可呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.83,0:04:04.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么干脆地就答应了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.06,0:04:07.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔也应该提出一点反驳意见吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.01,0:04:10.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起到处乱转去寻找外星人或者UMA
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.01,0:04:10.54,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（UMA：Unidentified Mysterious Animals，未知生物）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.78,0:04:12.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为这个活动要健康得多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.43,0:04:16.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  这个比赛什么时候开始？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.56,0:04:17.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个星期天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.67,0:04:18.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不就是后天吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.81,0:04:20.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎么说时间也太紧了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.43,0:04:22.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我已经报名了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.64,0:04:23.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你放心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.98,0:04:26.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队伍名称我已经报好是「SOS团」了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.89,0:04:28.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里我可是决不会出错的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.90,0:04:33.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他的4个队员你打算从哪里挖啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.39,0:04:36.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要随便逮几个在那些到处闲晃的人不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.90,0:04:38.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是认真这么说的么…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.23,0:04:41.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  你先别轻举妄动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.39,0:04:45.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之…谷口和国木田好像满闲的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.61,0:04:46.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些也行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.83,0:04:49.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她用「那些」来称呼同班同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.70,0:04:52.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…还剩下两个人吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.87,0:04:55.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问…如果我的朋友也可以的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.04,0:04:56.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就也算上那个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.81,0:04:57.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像什么人都可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.16,0:04:58.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.22,0:05:00.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝比奈学姐的朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.86,0:05:02.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有点放心不下了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.30,0:05:03.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么「时候」  什么「地方」交的朋友啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.91,0:05:05.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.77,0:05:07.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在这个时间…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.97,0:05:10.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在班上认识的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.63,0:05:11.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我也来推荐一个人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.33,0:05:15.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际上  我认识的一个人对我们的事很感兴趣…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.88,0:05:16.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后的人选由我来想办法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.77,0:05:20.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然决定好了就马上来特训吧！特训！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.52,0:05:22.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特训？现在就开始？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.74,0:05:23.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.53,0:05:24.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.50,0:05:25.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.36,0:05:33.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是我们就要去参加棒球比赛了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.48,0:05:34.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.87,0:05:36.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个答案很简单
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.12,0:05:39.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是  只不过是因为春日她…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.65,0:05:41.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点烦闷而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.20,0:05:44.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  打扰一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.35,0:05:45.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这个地方借给我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.91,0:05:47.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有棒球用具也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.58,0:05:49.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？你说什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.28,0:05:52.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们必须要赶快进行棒球训练嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.77,0:05:53.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们比较碍事  闪开吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.96,0:05:55.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们怎么可能答应啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.49,0:05:56.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么关系嘛！只借一阵子就好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.98,0:05:58.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧  实玖{\fe128\fnDFMaruMoji-W7\b0\fs24}瑠{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.91,0:06:02.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.69,0:06:06.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是容易被看穿的青春时期
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.73,0:06:09.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么先打个一千棒！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.98,0:06:10.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.18,0:06:21.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这球上可寄托了SOS团的未来！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.71,0:06:23.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我好好接住！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.47,0:06:27.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次听说我们的未来原来是寄托在这么小的一个球上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.18,0:06:37.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来一次！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.26,0:06:39.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实玖{\fe128\fnDFMaruMoji-W7\b0\fs24}瑠{\r}  要来了哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.20,0:06:44.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.72,0:06:50.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.07,0:06:51.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还站得起来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.59,0:06:54.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿虚  不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.71,0:06:57.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果和我感情这么好的话  又会…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.17,0:07:01.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！阿虚！实玖{\fe128\fnDFMaruMoji-W7\b0\fs24}瑠{\r}！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.14,0:07:02.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我回来！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.79,0:07:03.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们受伤退场！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.82,0:07:05.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.03,0:07:07.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面棒球社的给我补上去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.16,0:07:09.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我们要…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.41,0:07:17.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  今天就到此为止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.46,0:07:21.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是令人吃惊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.88,0:07:24.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的正好是打了一千棒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.58,0:07:27.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是连这个都能数得一清二楚的你比较令我吃惊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.71,0:07:29.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  长门
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.03,0:07:33.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比赛当天能不能让老天下场雨？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.47,0:07:35.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是能让比赛中止的那种大雨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.83,0:07:36.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是不能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.20,0:07:38.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不推荐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.96,0:07:39.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.56,0:07:41.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对局部性的环境资料进行篡改
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.07,0:07:45.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有对行星生态系统造成后遗症的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.00,0:07:47.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后遗症是…大约多久以后会发作？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.76,0:07:49.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几百年到一万年
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.03,0:07:53.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还是别这么做比较好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.39,0:07:55.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.48,0:08:02.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样  比赛当天来临了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.79,0:08:05.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…其实不来临也没什么问题的说…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.40,0:08:09.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是阿虚？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.96,0:08:11.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我经常听实玖{\fe128\fnDFMaruMoji-W7\b0\fs24}瑠{\r}提起你呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.34,0:08:13.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.62,0:08:14.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.83,0:08:17.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  这位是我的朋友鹤屋…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.69,0:08:19.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是谷口  请多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.34,0:08:21.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是国木田
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.78,0:08:24.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀～阿虚是我的好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.12,0:08:25.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的请求我实在没办法拒绝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.55,0:08:26.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.55,0:08:27.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}是谷口和国木田对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.91,0:08:29.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}我记住了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.62,0:08:30.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}这是我们的光荣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.09,0:08:28.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿虚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.57,0:08:30.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.05,0:08:34.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在想什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.64,0:08:36.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种家伙你也想让她上场打球？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.06,0:08:38.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说「那种家伙」也太失礼了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.74,0:08:40.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说可也是我的妹妹哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.72,0:08:44.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她自我介绍说是「小学五年级生  现在10岁」哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.46,0:08:47.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个坦率到无法联想到是你妹妹一般的好孩子呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.31,0:08:52.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过重点在于我们参加的可是一般年龄层的棒球赛！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.38,0:08:53.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是青少年级的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.00,0:08:55.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啊春日小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.66,0:08:57.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才会把妹妹带来啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.22,0:08:59.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然说本来就不可能打赢的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.06,0:09:01.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这可是春日搞出来的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.64,0:09:03.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果一不小心真的最终胜出了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.34,0:09:04.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会变成超级麻烦的事情的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.36,0:09:07.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果混一个小学五年级生进去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.34,0:09:09.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样能赢才奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.13,0:09:11.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.28,0:09:13.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好稍微放一下水
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.08,0:09:16.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果赢得太狠也就太不给对手面子了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.22,0:09:17.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像她还真的想要打赢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.72,0:09:23.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.98,0:09:25.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没有决定打击顺序和守备位置呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.08,0:09:26.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.82,0:09:28.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经想好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.87,0:09:31.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这个来决定！没有意见了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.44,0:09:33.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有打击的顺序和防守的位置两种
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.05,0:09:36.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外我是投手和一棒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.90,0:09:39.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想好的只有决定的方法吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.72,0:09:41.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么  你有什么不满意的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.95,0:09:43.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是民主的方法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.76,0:09:46.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古希腊可是还用抽签来选政治家呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.82,0:09:51.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别把古希腊的政治制度\N和现代日本的草地棒球打击顺序混为一谈好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.67,0:09:53.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且只有你可以按照兴趣来选择
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.83,0:09:55.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算什么民主啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.30,0:09:57.00,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字      守备位置\N一棒  凉宫春日  投手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.10,0:09:57.80,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二棒  实玖{\fe128\fnDFMaruMoji-W7\b0\fs20}瑠{\r}    右外野\N三棒  有希      中间手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.90,0:09:58.60,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四棒  阿虚      二垒手\N五棒  虚妹      左外野
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.70,0:09:59.40,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六棒  古泉      捕手\N七棒  国木田    一垒手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.50,0:10:00.20,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八棒  鹤屋      三垒手\N九棒  谷口      游击手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.05,0:09:56.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  也好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.10,0:09:58.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来能够更快地回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.06,0:10:00.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为刚刚听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.76,0:10:03.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一场的对手是叫做「上上原海盗」的大学生球队
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.03,0:10:06.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是本届大赛的种子队伍之一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.62,0:10:09.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为只要得分相差10分就会提前结束比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.35,0:10:13.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就开始准备回家应该也不算早了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.78,0:10:16.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fe128\fnDFMaruMoji-W7\b0\fs24}Play Ball{\r}（比赛开始）！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.86,0:10:32.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他投的球完全没什么好怕的！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.07,0:10:34.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都跟上来吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.50,0:10:39.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.09,0:10:40.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fe128\fnDFMaruMoji-W7\b0\fs24}Strike{\r}（好球）！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.18,0:10:44.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这厮对着朝比奈学姐投得是什么该死的球！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.33,0:10:45.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我打到她身上一个看看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.22,0:10:46.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上就去跟你们群殴！把这里变成群殴狂欢！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.00,0:10:49.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fe128\fnDFMaruMoji-W7\b0\fs24}Strike{\r}（好球）！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.79,0:10:50.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实玖{\fe128\fnDFMaruMoji-W7\b0\fs24}瑠{\r}！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.19,0:10:53.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使劲打啊！使劲！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.44,0:10:55.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fe128\fnDFMaruMoji-W7\b0\fs24}Struck Out{\r}（三振出局）！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.91,0:10:59.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！为什么不挥棒啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.97,0:11:00.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fe128\fnDFMaruMoji-W7\b0\fs24}Strike{\r}（好球）！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.91,0:11:01.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fe128\fnDFMaruMoji-W7\b0\fs24}Strike{\r}（好球）！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.70,0:11:03.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fe128\fnDFMaruMoji-W7\b0\fs24}Struck Out{\r}（三振出局）！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.52,0:11:06.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有希！如果不挥棒的话不是就更不会打中了吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.90,0:11:10.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿虚  你一定要打中啊！你可是四棒！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.90,0:11:10.12,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（一般四棒的位置会安排打击力最强的队员，称之为强打或强棒）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.54,0:11:13.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在期待我这个抽签决定的四棒做些什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.10,0:11:16.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fe128\fnDFMaruMoji-W7\b0\fs24}Strike{\r}（好球）！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.60,0:11:18.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春日是面对这种球打出长打的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.46,0:11:20.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fe128\fnDFMaruMoji-W7\b0\fs24}Strike{\r}（好球）！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.39,0:11:29.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fe128\fnDFMaruMoji-W7\b0\fs24}Struck Out{\r}（三振出局）！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.18,0:11:32.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白痴！你在做什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.69,0:11:32.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.21,0:11:36.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,严防死守吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.92,0:11:38.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好——！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.51,0:11:42.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fe128\fnDFMaruMoji-W7\b0\fs24}Play{\r}（比赛继续）！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.62,0:11:45.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fe128\fnDFMaruMoji-W7\b0\fs24}Strike{\r}（好球）！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.72,0:11:49.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fe128\fnDFMaruMoji-W7\b0\fs24}Strike{\r}（好球）！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.72,0:11:51.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fe128\fnDFMaruMoji-W7\b0\fs24}Struck Out{\r}（三振出局）！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.32,0:11:53.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fe128\fnDFMaruMoji-W7\b0\fs24}Nice pitch{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.81,0:11:55.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游刃有余啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.34,0:12:02.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fe128\fnDFMaruMoji-W7\b0\fs24}Foul ball{\r}（界外球）！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.64,0:12:20.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为她只会冲着好球区投直球而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.58,0:12:22.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦被人看出来当然会被打中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.08,0:12:27.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我们守备的漏洞比热带大草原上蚁巢的还要多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.34,0:12:28.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竹筐一样！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.81,0:12:31.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一回合总算是把失分控制在2分
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.26,0:12:35.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是因为对方的胜利女神来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.61,0:12:38.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星期天谁都希望休息一下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.64,0:12:41.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来  第二轮的攻势也是毫无悬念地结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.64,0:12:39.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\fe128\fnDFMaruMoji-W7\b0\fs24}Struck Out{\r}（三振出局）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.37,0:12:39.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\fe128\fnDFMaruMoji-W7\b0\fs24}Struck Out{\r}（三振出局）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.05,0:12:40.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\fe128\fnDFMaruMoji-W7\b0\fs24}Struck Out{\r}（三振出局）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.09,0:12:44.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后又很干脆地被对方拿下了几分
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.38,0:12:47.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来下一回合就可以结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.53,0:12:51.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fe128\fnDFMaruMoji-W7\b0\fs24}Out{\r}（出局）！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.97,0:12:55.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太难了吧  光是让球棒打到球就用尽全力了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.23,0:12:59.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是需要那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.96,0:13:02.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先{\fe128\fnDFMaruMoji-W7\b0\fs24}Time{\r}（暂停）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.01,0:13:05.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？等  等一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.13,0:13:08.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凉宫同学…不要啊——
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.81,0:13:11.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了！快点给我脱好换衣服！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.81,0:13:16.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好合适哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.81,0:13:17.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实玖{\fe128\fnDFMaruMoji-W7\b0\fs24}瑠{\r}  可以拍下来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.79,0:13:20.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是绑个马尾比较好啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.07,0:13:26.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  来加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.75,0:13:28.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？那个  要怎么做呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.70,0:13:29.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这么做～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.15,0:13:32.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  大声加油吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.65,0:13:35.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各  各位！请打中吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.56,0:13:37.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你们了  加油吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.06,0:13:39.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的～包在我身上！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.11,0:13:41.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fe128\fnDFMaruMoji-W7\b0\fs24}Struck Out{\r}（三振出局）！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.36,0:13:42.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种球果然还是打不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.28,0:13:45.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  反正也没指望你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.48,0:14:01.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安全上垒！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.50,0:14:04.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实玖{\fe128\fnDFMaruMoji-W7\b0\fs24}瑠{\r}！这次一定要打中哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.59,0:14:05.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}上吧！实玖{\fe128\fnDFMaruMoji-W7\b0\fs24}瑠{\r}！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.38,0:14:05.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}请加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.36,0:14:10.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fe128\fnDFMaruMoji-W7\b0\fs24}Strike{\r}（好球）！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.19,0:14:12.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实玖{\fe128\fnDFMaruMoji-W7\b0\fs24}瑠{\r}！这个啊  用这个！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.26,0:14:14.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在搞什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.09,0:14:18.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道这样能让对方投手的MP减少吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.99,0:14:21.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来好像是在打暗号呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.00,0:14:23.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们决定过什么暗号吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.75,0:14:24.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.93,0:14:28.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我想那大概是叫她用抢分战术吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.93,0:14:28.83,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（抢分战术：跑者在三垒时，打击手使用牺牲打令跑者得以回本垒的战术）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.15,0:14:31.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二人出局还打抢分战术的暗号？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.44,0:14:35.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是那个永世教练也会用更常识性的战术吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.44,0:14:35.94,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（永世教练：指巨人队的长岛教练，\N巨人队时代教练都由长岛家的人担任而得名。被很多球迷厌恶）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.59,0:14:41.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是发现了朝比奈打中球的几率基本上是零
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.61,0:14:43.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会是因此做出意义不明的暗号
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.78,0:14:45.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故意让对方看透
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.54,0:14:48.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许会令内野手出现失误
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.87,0:14:54.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是希望朝比奈同学用牺牲打打中球的话也能有办法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.38,0:14:56.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然完全被人家看透了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.65,0:14:59.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fe128\fnDFMaruMoji-W7\b0\fs24}Strike{\r}（好球）！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.32,0:15:01.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fe128\fnDFMaruMoji-W7\b0\fs24}Struck Out{\r}（三振出局）！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.59,0:15:03.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实玖{\fe128\fnDFMaruMoji-W7\b0\fs24}瑠{\r}  你给我过来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.55,0:15:04.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后咬紧牙关！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.48,0:15:06.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是惩罚  惩罚！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.72,0:15:09.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要让大家看看你这张可笑的脸！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.92,0:15:11.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.69,0:15:12.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是白痴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.06,0:15:16.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是打出莫名其妙暗号的你不好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.77,0:15:19.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己去盗本垒不好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.60,0:15:30.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大事不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.63,0:15:32.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我虽然不想听  不过你姑且说说看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.39,0:15:35.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个前所未有大规模的封闭空间开始产生了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.11,0:15:38.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还正在以非常快的速度扩大着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.31,0:15:43.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要凉宫同学的心情不恢复  它就会持续扩大
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.76,0:15:45.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「那个」也就会继续大肆破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.75,0:15:46.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.87,0:15:48.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是因为打输了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.06,0:15:50.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个不懂事的小鬼！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.14,0:15:52.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然你说得好像是别人的事情一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.92,0:15:55.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这和你也有很大的关系哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.18,0:15:59.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为决定打击顺序的时候我们不是抽签了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.28,0:16:02.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而作为结果  你是四棒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.09,0:16:04.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不觉得高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.55,0:16:06.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为凉宫同学这样希望
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.40,0:16:08.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你才成为了第四棒打击手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.50,0:16:09.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这并非偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.64,0:16:13.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  你完全没有起到四棒的作用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.98,0:16:15.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以她失望了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.61,0:16:16.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.87,0:16:21.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  这一回合尽全力令比赛不要提前结束吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.85,0:16:23.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果现在比赛结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.93,0:16:25.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就等同于世界末日来临
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.94,0:16:27.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！要开始了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.99,0:16:30.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何  都要把失分控制在两分以内
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.69,0:16:38.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人出局  跑者在一  二垒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.64,0:16:40.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在零对九
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.33,0:16:42.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一分就会强制结束比赛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.33,0:16:46.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来这边了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.10,0:16:50.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要赶上啊  要赶上啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.60,0:16:52.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好厉害哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.50,0:16:55.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fe128\fnDFMaruMoji-W7\b0\fs24}Nice Play{\r}!干得不错嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.24,0:16:56.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是我的好友！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.67,0:17:03.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续刚才的话题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.45,0:17:04.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的脸凑得太近了  什么事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.00,0:17:08.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你上次和凉宫同学一起到那个世界去的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.90,0:17:10.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怎么回来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.59,0:17:12.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别让我想起那件事来！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.50,0:17:16.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果用那一招的话  也许又能够顺利解决了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.23,0:17:16.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.22,0:17:18.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想也是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.07,0:17:21.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就用些能够确保胜利的方法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.60,0:17:25.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们和她之间的利害关系应该也是一致的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.55,0:17:31.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长门同学终于也…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.98,0:17:33.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她做了什么吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.03,0:17:35.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她好像在咏唱咒文
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.01,0:17:38.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咒文？那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.83,0:17:41.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…这是禁止谈论的事项
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.92,0:17:44.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咒文吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.81,0:17:59.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害啊！你怎么有这么大的力气？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.29,0:18:03.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个  对属性信息作了能力提升改写
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.18,0:18:03.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.96,0:18:05.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制导模式
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.76,0:18:08.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞得好远！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.13,0:18:11.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此  制导模式啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.21,0:18:14.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  乱来也要有点限度嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.51,0:18:25.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么说  再这样下去就糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.73,0:18:27.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在各种意义上…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.68,0:18:29.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.00,0:18:31.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.26,0:18:32.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fe128\fnDFMaruMoji-W7\b0\fs24}Strike{\r}（好球）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.83,0:18:33.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fe128\fnDFMaruMoji-W7\b0\fs24}Strike{\r}（好球）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.26,0:18:33.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fe128\fnDFMaruMoji-W7\b0\fs24}Strike{\r}（好球）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.32,0:18:38.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才忘记说了  第一场比赛时间限制为90分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.73,0:18:40.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以已经没有下一回合了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.77,0:18:43.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要守住这一回合  我们就获胜了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.95,0:18:45.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗？就这样获胜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.90,0:18:47.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不获胜不行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.81,0:18:52.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏如此  封闭空间的扩大速度似乎已经降下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.08,0:18:56.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过如果在这里被对方逆转局势的话可就再见滑铁卢了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.34,0:19:00.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过猜那个时候春日心情如何也没有意义了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.32,0:19:01.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我有个提议
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.80,0:19:04.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.65,0:19:05.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常当真
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.54,0:19:08.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要把这一回合的失分控制在最低
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.84,0:19:10.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有这个方法了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.05,0:19:12.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.86,0:19:17.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fe128\fnDFMaruMoji-W7\b0\fs24}Ball{\r}（坏球）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.76,0:19:20.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！你给我好好投！难得我和你交换位置
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.92,0:19:22.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果输了的话就罚你请所有人吃饭！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.09,0:19:24.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.63,0:19:27.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么说  我投的球可是负担着全世界的命运啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.51,0:19:30.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…这个世界还真是不值钱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.16,0:19:36.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fe128\fnDFMaruMoji-W7\b0\fs24}Strike{\r}（好球）！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.14,0:19:39.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于这{\fe128\fnDFMaruMoji-W7\b0\fs24}Mysterious Ball{\r}（命名：我）的缘故
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.49,0:19:41.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来世界不需要被毁灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.56,0:19:45.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fe128\fnDFMaruMoji-W7\b0\fs24}S…Strike two{\r}（两好球）！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.67,0:19:46.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fe128\fnDFMaruMoji-W7\b0\fs24}Struck Out{\r}（三振出局）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.88,0:19:50.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来的打击手也很无聊地被三球三振了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.15,0:19:50.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fe128\fnDFMaruMoji-W7\b0\fs24}Struck Out{\r}（三振出局）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.34,0:19:53.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕会已经成为最后的打击手的那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.23,0:19:54.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在也已经两好球了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.53,0:19:54.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fe128\fnDFMaruMoji-W7\b0\fs24}Strike two{\r}（两好球）！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.62,0:19:57.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿虚  还有一球  决出胜负吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.32,0:19:59.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你不说这球也会决定胜负吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.97,0:20:01.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了  上上原海盗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.71,0:20:05.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侥幸！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.62,0:20:06.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不死三振了！长门！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.62,0:20:08.40,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（不死三振：在一垒无人情况下，\N捕手未能接到应该能将打击手三振的球时，打击手安全冲上一垒）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.19,0:20:08.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去捡起球来投过去！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.91,0:20:13.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.81,0:20:17.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二垒！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.84,0:20:17.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边这边！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.85,0:20:19.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.40,0:20:19.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.80,0:20:20.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.37,0:20:24.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.01,0:20:28.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们这一群人稍微有点超乎常理
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.58,0:20:30.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fe128\fnDFMaruMoji-W7\b0\fs24}Ga…game and set{\r}（比赛结束）！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.58,0:20:30.11,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（日文的省略读法读作「Game set」）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.90,0:20:34.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然因为长门的作弊式魔法我们打赢了这一场…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.27,0:20:37.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二场要怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.28,0:20:40.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果就这样继续打第二场的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.32,0:20:42.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些对不起上上原海盗  而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.31,0:20:47.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我也差不多该去给「同伴」们帮忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.72,0:20:49.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话人数也不够了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.79,0:20:50.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弃权吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.77,0:20:51.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样比较好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.28,0:20:55.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来不能让凉宫同学闲下来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.09,0:20:58.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就作为今后的课题吧  有研究的价值
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.71,0:21:01.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也玩够了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.54,0:21:03.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古泉说有急事要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.96,0:21:07.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的腿和手臂也都累得动不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.28,0:21:15.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你觉得可以  那就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.27,0:21:17.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有些饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.82,0:21:19.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吃午饭吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.76,0:21:20.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的好的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.03,0:21:23.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的太感谢你了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.38,0:21:24.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.64,0:21:25.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我先告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.50,0:21:27.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.07,0:21:29.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于你这根球棒…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.18,0:21:34.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己都没有注意到过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.55,0:21:36.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来我有打棒球的天分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.23,0:21:39.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家尽量多吃点吧  今天阿虚请客～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.51,0:21:41.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  也好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.89,0:21:44.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我口袋里也有一笔临时收入了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.94,0:21:47.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我衷心期盼上上原海盗队能拿下傲人战绩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.89,0:21:54.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐生！好好打！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.37,0:22:01.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉来迟啦～！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.49,0:22:03.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  这次参加哪个好？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.71,0:22:06.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,足球和美式橄榄球都是多少人参加的运动？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.08,0:22:09.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只用之前的那些人够吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.62,0:22:11.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一面看着春日最美丽的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.24,0:22:15.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开始考虑哪个是人数最少的运动
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.13,0:22:18.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美式橄榄球…不！去给我打门球吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.13,0:22:18.65,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（一种只需要5个人的球类运动）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.41,0:23:38.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  神秘信号  嗡……
